arts.ttl: Go Ahead Eagles strike late to deny Fortuna Sittard
arts.sum: The Eredivisie 2025/26 season got underway on Friday with Go Ahead Eagles earning a 2-2 draw away to Fortuna Sittard. After a slow start, it was Go Ahead Eagles who took the lead with Shawn Adewoye sliding a cross into his own net. arts.ttl: Go Ahead Eagles to be without key playmaker for Eredivisie opener against Fortuna Sittard
arts.sum: Go Ahead Eagles will be without Jakob Breum for the opening fixture of the new Eredivisie season after the Danish star sustained an ankle injury.
